court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION Miscellaneous Petition No.965 of 1978 The Nila Products Limited .. .. Petitioners v/s. V. Prasad & ors. .. .. Respondents None present for parties. ---- CORAM : DR. D.Y. CHANDRACHUD, J. DATED : st July, 2009 P.C.: .The Registry has placed the Petition before this Court for hearing since it is numbered as a Miscellaneous Petition. From the reliefs sought, it would appear that the Petition was filed in 1978 under Article 226 of the Constitution of India. . Accordingly, the Registry is directed to place the Petition before appropriate Bench according to the roster of work after verifying that the Petition has not already been disposed of. (DR. D.Y. CHANDRACHUD, J.)
